name: Community
description: During my first year as a cryptoartist I found myself every day in front of dozens and dozens of accounts that asked me to pay for some advertising, accounts that on the other hand boast the name of the community, the same ones whose only the aim is to make money by pissing on the true meaning of community: that of the union of mutual help, support and sometimes even criticism and discussion. To all those who see cryptoart only as a means of economic speculation: the day when the roles are reversed and we will piss on your head, be careful, be scared
